ion, but got empty.","next/no-assign-module-variable","Do not assign to the variable `module`. See: https://nextjs.org/docs/messages/no-assign-module-variable","VariableDeclaration","unused-imports/no-unused-vars","'result' is assigned a value but never used. Allowed unused vars must match /^_/u.","unusedVar","next/no-img-element","Using `<img>` could result in slower LCP and higher bandwidth. Consider using `<Image />` from `next/image` or a custom image loader to automatically optimize images. This may incur additional usage or cost from your provider. See: https://nextjs.org/docs/messages/no-img-element","JSXOpeningElement","react/no-array-index-key","Do not use item index in the array as its key.","Identifier","noArrayIndexKey","react-dom/no-missing-button-type","Add missing 'type' attribute on 'button' component.","noMissingButtonType",["4517","4518","4519"],["4520","4521","4522"],["4523","4524","4525"],["4526","4527","4528"],["4529","4530","4531"],["4532","4533","4534"],["4535","4536","4537"],["4538","4539","4540"],["4541","4542","4543"],["4544","4545","4546"],["4547","4548","4549"],["4550","4551","4552"],["4553","4554","4555"],["4556","4557","4558"],["4559","4560","4561"],"react-hooks/exhaustive-deps","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'loadPatients'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.","ArrayExpression",["4562"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'loadMedia'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["4563"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'loadQuotes'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["4564"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'loadNotes'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["4565"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'loadInProgressTasks'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["4566"],"no-useless-catch","Unnecessary try/catch wrapper.","TryStatement","unnecessaryCatch",["4567","4568","4569"],["4570","4571","4572"],["4